  "description": "morphGlide 0.92, portamento 0.7. Every legato note is a biological transformation — the body does not move to the new pitch, it becomes it. owl_bodyLevel high: the sine foundation witnesses the metamorphosis without participating. Divisions ÷3 and ÷6 create a tense hybrid of inharmonic color and octave grounding. Play slowly.",
